Volcano plot Online Presentation

Jiacheng Lou
2020-01-29

Idea

The main idea of the application is to provide usefule interface for Volcano plot. It could be use for drawing your favorite Volcano plot.

Tools Detail

Tools Parameters

  • Cutoff of Foldchange - Change Vertical dotted line
  • Cutoff of Padj - Change horizontal dotted line
  • Input Number of Xlim - X axle max range
  • Input Number of Ylim - Y axle max range
  • Select Color panel - Change Plot color panel

Input Data Example

Vol.data<-read.csv("VolResult-3.csv",header = T)
